Class ReducedStateSpace

  • java.lang.Object
    • statespace.StateSpace
      • statespace.ReducedStateSpace
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<State>, java.util.Iterator<State>

    public class ReducedStateSpace
extends StateSpace
implements java.lang.Iterable<State>, java.util.Iterator<State>
    For this StateSpace we make the assumption that the predator stays in a fixed position and only the prey moves.
